          EXTREAL_SUM_IMAGE (\i. g (i + N)) (count (n + N - N))’
 >- (MATCH_MP_TAC EXTREAL_SUM_IMAGE_OFFSET >> rw [] \\
    ‘n < N \/ N <= n’ by rw [] >- rw [] \\
    ‘n = n - N + N’ by rw [] >> POP_ORW >> METIS_TAC [])
 >> Rewr'
