          ONCE_ASM_REWRITE_TAC [] \\
         `0 < r` by METIS_TAC [extreal_of_num_def, extreal_lt_eq] \\
         `?n. inv (&SUC n) < r` by METIS_TAC [REAL_ARCH_INV_SUC] \\
          MATCH_MP_TAC le_trans >> Q.EXISTS_TAC `f n + 1 / &SUC n` \\
